{"name": "mag-tools", "metadata": {"name": "mag-tools", "version": "0.1.8", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "http://gitlab.magnetitech.com:8088/sources/frame/py-frame/mag_tools.git", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "\u5e38\u7528\u5de5\u5177\u5305", "upload_time": 1733123642}, "documentation": ["# \u57fa\u672c\u5e93 Mag_Tools\r\n## \u5b89\u88c5\u4f9d\u8d56\u5e93\r\n- Rust\u7f16\u8bd1\u5668\r\n    \u8bbf\u95ee Rust \u5b98\u7f51 \u5e76\u4e0b\u8f7d\u9002\u7528\u4e8e Windows \u7684\u5b89\u88c5\u7a0b\u5e8f\uff0c\u6216\u8005\u76f4\u63a5\u8fd0\u884c\u4ee5\u4e0b\u547d\u4ee4\uff1a\r\n    ```Bash\r\n        Invoke-WebRequest -Uri https://sh.rustup.rs -OutFile rustup-init.exe\r\n    ```\r\n    ```Bash\r\n        .\\rustup-init.exe\r\n    ```\r\n   \u6dfb\u52a0 Rust \u7f16\u8bd1\u5668\u7684\u8def\u5f84\uff08\u901a\u5e38\u662f C:\\Users\\\u4f60\u7684\u7528\u6237\u540d\\.cargo\\bin\uff09\r\n- \u5b89\u88c5\u4f9d\u8d56\u9879\r\n  ```Bash\r\n    pip install --upgrade pip\r\n    pip install maturin\r\n  ```\r\n## \u53d1\u5e03\u5e93 \r\n- \u521b\u5efa\u865a\u62df\u73af\u5883\r\n    ```Bash\r\n    python -m venv venv\r\n- \u6fc0\u6d3b\u865a\u62df\u73af\u5883\r\n    ```Bash\r\n    venv\\Scripts\\activate\r\n    ```\r\n- \u5b89\u88c5\u4f9d\u8d56\u9879\r\n    ```Bash\r\n      pip install -r requirements.txt\r\n    ```\r\n- \u7f16\u8f91\u6253\u5305\r\n    ```Bash\r\n      python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel\r\n    ```\r\n- \u672c\u5730\u5b89\u88c5\u5e93\r\n    ```Bash\r\n       pip install dist/mag_tools-0.1-py3-none-any.whl \r\n    ```\r\n  - \u4e0a\u4f20\u5305\r\n    ```Bash\r\n      twine upload dist/*\r\n    ```\r\n## \u914d\u7f6e API Token\r\n- \u83b7\u53d6API Token\r\n- \u914d\u7f6e.pypirc \u6587\u4ef6\uff1a \u5728\u7528\u6237\u4e3b\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u521b\u5efa .pypirc \u6587\u4ef6\uff0c\u5e76\u6dfb\u52a0\u4ee5\u4e0b\u5185\u5bb9